title: Put Yourself in a State of Awe
itunes:title: Put Yourself in a State of Awe
description:
Episode 140 - Everything is amazing and people fail to notice it. We live in the most amazing time in human history but people are still unhappy. The secret is that the quality of your life will be dictated by what you choose to focus on. In this episode I talk in depth on that topic and how you can change your focus.
